# Keyboard Shortcuts

The photo gallery application supports the following keyboard shortcuts for improved user experience:

| Key Combination | Action |
|-----------------|--------|
| `/` | Focus search bar |
| `Esc` | Close modal/dialog |
| `←` `→` | Navigate between photos in gallery view |
| `Space` | Toggle fullscreen view |
| `+` / `-` | Zoom in/out when viewing photo details |
| `c` | Add current photo to cart |

These shortcuts are defined in the application to enhance navigation and user interaction.
